{
  "stem": "25831.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know that I did it well, but I thought so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he said, one year of social democracy has [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] disturbed Germany and one year of Bolshevism would have ruined it forever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In German it sounded like this, as spoken by Hitler, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Subsequently, a few days thereafter, the Reichstag Building, the parliament building, burned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A fire had been set there and the building really was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And five people, the arsonists, the suspected arsonists, were arrested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Two were Bulgarian communists with names I forgot, but they're mentioned in many books, the leader of the German Communist Party, a man by the name of Torgler, another person whose name I forgot, and a Dutch communist by the name of Van de Lubbe And Van de Lubbe was apprehended.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And his picture was shown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was in the Reichstag Building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He had a torch in his hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he readily confessed to having set fire to the Reichstag.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I mean, everybody knew he had been drugged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he had been promised all kinds of things, that he wouldn't be arrested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But he became the focus of the investigation and of the trial.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And a lengthy trial was held to show how fair the Nazis are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was given a defense counsel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I think the defense counsel was a rather prominent lawyer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But, needless to say, he was found guilty and he was executed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the other, the three Bulgarians-- the two Bulgarians and the man I can't remember were acquitted and they were asked to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And Torgler, the communist, was also found not guilty.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
